clipboard_import_dialog_title: Ingiza data za jedwali kama kazi ndogo za __task_or_project_name__

clipboard_import_invalid_option_value: Thamani batili ya __field__ __val__ katika mstari wa __line__ - sio chaguo halali. Uingizaji umesitishwa.

clipboard_import_please_select_source_da: Tafadhali chagua muundo wa tarehe chanzo.
